SECTION 1. The following sitios in the Municipality of Talibon, Province of Bohol, are declared as barrios of said municipality, to wit:

Sitio Nueva Esperanza as Barrio Esperanza;

Sitio Nueva Estrella as Barrio Estrella;

Sitio Mandawa as Barrio Mandawa;

Sitio Malingin as Barrio Malingin;

Sitio Maomawan as Barrio Maomawan;

Sitio Sagasa as Barrio Sagasa;

Sitio Burgos as Barrio Burgos;

Sitio Rizal as Barrio Rizal;

Sitio Tanghaligue as Barrio Tanghaligue;

Sitio Mahanay as Barrio Mahanay;

Sitio Hebale as Barrio Hebale;

Sitio Santo Niño as Barrio Santo Niño;

Sitio Santa Fe as Barrio Santa Fe;

Sitio Cantubod as Barrio Cantubod;

Sitio Remedios as Barrio Remedios;

Sitio Dagohoy as Barrio Dagohoy;

Sitio Zamora as Barrio Zamora;

Sitio San Roque as Barrio San Roque;

Sitio Sikatuna as Barrio Sikatuna;

Sitio Magsaysay as Barrio Magsaysay;

Sitio San Jose Sur as Barrio San Jose Sur;

Sitio Balintawak as Barrio Balintawak; and

Sitio Nonocnocan as Barrio Nonocnocan.

SEC. 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.

Enacted without Executive approval June 19, 1960.
